Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.96,0:00:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer the man, scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.47,0:00:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to join the Recon Corps,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.39,0:00:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and kill as many Titans as I can, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Erwin. I'll take responsibility for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell that to the higher-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong. It's not like I trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If he betrays us or goes berserk, I'll put him down without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Upstairs shouldn't have a problem with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody except me is suited for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll accept your application to the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are there really Titans that sided with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come on, it's obviously just a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:03:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The retake campaign might've failed, meaning lots of people from Wall Rose could be evacuating here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But then we're bound to have another food shortage...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What if the Titan that sided with humans joins up with the Rose refugees,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and they attack us together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is huge news! A Titan has sided with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We might even be able to retake Wall Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Say it! He's our savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Savior, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The common folk are always so irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They might even try to using him to incite rebellion against the Inner District.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As the Police, we must dispose of Eren Jaeger before that can happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let those freaks at the Recon Corps get their hands on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute the Supreme Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Pixis,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,some people consider it inappropriate for you, as Commander of the Garrison,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to be conversing privately with someone like me from the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, you're as stiff as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We merely ran into each other by \Nchance during our morning walks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we're already walking, we might as well chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard that the Police are also after Eren Jaeger?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They sent word yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A trial will be held.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The decision about whether the Police or the Recon Corps get Eren
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,has been entrusted to Zacklay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Zacklay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean Supreme Commander Dallis Zacklay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the man in charge of all three forces: the \NMilitary Police, the Garrison, and the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When making decisions, he considers only one method:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the cost-benefit analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, whether it's profitable or harmful to mankind overall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means he wouldn't hesitate to execute Eren right on the spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,if that were the verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to let him kill Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But unfortunately, more than a few in my Garrison fear Eren's powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can do is to argue my case against the Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can win?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have also prepared a proposition,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but its viability depends greatly on the way the trial progresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're planning to go in cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We of the Recon Corps are used to getting chills from our work outside the Walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't as stiff as you seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for such a nice stroll, Colonel Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren's being put on trial? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.19,0:06:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's about deciding how to deal with Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What does {\i1}that{\i0}  mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably deciding whether he lives or dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa Ackerman! Armin Arlert!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been ordered to appear at the trial this afternoon as witnesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. May I use the toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You just went earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Understand the situation you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Monster? I guess they're not wrong about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I so scary that they need to restrain me this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shouldn't be that surprised. I don't really understand all this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should just be happy that I haven't been killed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those two weren't scared of me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are they doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What happened to everybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be patient for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll try to sort things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How many days have passed since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't have to live my whole life like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Eren, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay? Feeling filthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you wait for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You can finally leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Though you'll have to wear these.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from the Recon Corps. Major Hanji Zoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fellow Major Mike Zacharias.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:09:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, he just has this habit of sniffing people at their first meeting, then laughing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't read much into it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's skilled enough to become a major, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we chatted all the time away. We're already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.61,0:09:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you're better off without an explanation too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have a choice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but to trust you blindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A courtroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I was being held under the courthouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Move along!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kneel down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are these people here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this trial even about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now then, let us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You are Eren Jaeger, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're a soldier who vowed to devote his life to the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is an exceptional case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:11:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It is outside the bounds of common law, therefore we must convene a special court-martial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The final decision will be handed down by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We will deliberate upon whether you live or die as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do you have any objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,None, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're so cooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me say this straightforwardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Concealing your existence has proven impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless we publicize your existence in some way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we will have to face another threat besides the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This court is tasked with deciding which force will take custody of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the Military Police or the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,First, let us hear the proposition from the Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Nile Dawk, Chief of the Military Police. Our proposition is as follows:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We will examine Eren's body thoroughly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,then dispose of him as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fact that his Titan power repelled the last attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,However, his character induces disturbances that may even lead to a rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore he shall provide us with as much intelligence as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,then he'll become a martyr for mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a vermin that breached and \Ninfiltrated the sacred Walls of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's from the Church of the Walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Five years ago no one even took them seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}He should be killed here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They've come a long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Priest Nick, quiet, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, let us hear the proposition from the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Colonel Erwin Smith, head of the Thirteenth Battalion of the Recon Corps. Our proposition is as follows:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We will accept Eren as a formal member of the Recon Corps,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and recapture Wall Maria by using his Titan power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Using his abilities, we can retake Wall Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe the priorities are clearly apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, from where do you intend to launch that operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pixis, I believe the gate at Trost was sealed for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It'll probably never be opened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We would like to start from Calanes in the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We will approach Shiganshina on a new route.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Shouldn't we seal all the gates now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Colossal Titan can only destroy the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If we fortify those areas, they won't be able to attack us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you puppet of the traders' guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Using that Titan strength, we can return to Wall Maria once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fed up with you playing hero all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk a lot, pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who says the Titans will wait until you can lock up all the gates?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say "we", are you referring to your little friends who you plan to get fat with?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you even see that people are starving because we don't have enough land?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're only suggesting that if we sealed the gates, we'd be saf—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of your insolence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you even suggest doing such a thing to the sacred Wall Rose, given unto us by God?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You look upon the greatness of the Walls, which transcends human understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and you still can't see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was their fault that it took so long to fortify the defenses of the Walls...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They have the money and the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You speak blasphemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no place for a priest to speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Argue about your individual beliefs and opinions somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:15:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Jaeger, let me ask you this:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you keep fighting for the sake of mankind as a soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and also use your Titan power for the same goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the report from Trost it says:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"He swung his fist at Mikasa Ackerman right after becoming a Titan."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He doesn't remember that he lost control?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to lie in a report?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind gains nothing from hiding such a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Mikasa Ackerman here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that after he transformed, Jaeger attacked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You must tell the truth. For Eren's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Titans are Titans after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I tried to kill Mikasa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I{\i0}  did?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that, he also saved my life twice while in Titan form.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was about to fall prey to a Titan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,he fought them off and defended me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The second time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,he protected me and Armin from cannon fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I entreat you to consider these facts as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe this testimony is too \Nemotionally-biased to be accepted in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa Ackerman lost her parents at a young age, and she was taken in by Jaeger's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we uncovered some surprising details regarding those events.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:17:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren Jaeger and Mikasa Ackerman were nine years old at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They murdered all three robber-kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You might call this justifiable self-defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't help but feel disturbed by the \Nfundamental lack of humanity in their actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we really trust him with the fate, funds, and manpower of mankind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! He's probably a Titan who infiltrated us disguised as a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.47,0:17:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Her too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we be sure she's human?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! We should dissect her just in case!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Maybe I {\i1}am{\i0} a monster, but she has nothing to do with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As if we could believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fact!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're defending her? She must be one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep using mere speculation just to make the water flow your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, you've never even seen a Titan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So why are you so afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I'm gonna say it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll tell them what I think!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If those with strength don't fight, who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're too scared to fight for your lives, then at least don't hinder me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You cowards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.32,0:18:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up and let me shoulder it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just my personal opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but pain is the best tool for discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to be educated by words.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You need training.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've fallen low enough that you're easy to kick around, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Levi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he starts raging and turns into a Titan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were going to dissect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As I heard it, when he turned into a Titan, he killed 20 other Titans before his strength ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If he were an enemy, he might cause more trouble than that intel's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He still can't stand against me though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you on the other hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you who persecute him, think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Supreme Commander, I have a proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren's Titan power has a multitude of \Nuncertainties and unknown elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It is exceedingly dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So why don't we put Eren under Captain Levi's command
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and send them on a mission outside the Walls?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether Eren can control his Titan power,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and whether he may be of benefit to mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,should be decided based on the results of that mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch over Eren Jaeger...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do that, Levi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can definitely kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is it'll either be all or nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so mean of him. It must hurt a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about doing that. But as a result, we got you for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We were able to play our trump cards at the most effective moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pain was worth our gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I understand it was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.57,0:21:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:21:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You could've at least held back a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You even broke his tooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:21:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pick that up. It's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an important sample for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, I bet you're glad you won't be dissected by freaks like her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't put me in the same league as them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't kill Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.53,0:22:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, may I see the inside of your mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,His tooth... already grew back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.60,0:24:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eren finally gets assigned to the Recon Corps he so admired.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.37,0:24:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}He discovers it to be a group of people who demand change,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.94,0:24:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}as well as a haven for freaks and weirdos.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.85,0:24:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That is the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:01.94,Op 2 - TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,690)\fad(200,200)\blur1}Look, my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:04.46,Op 2 - TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,690)\fad(200,200)\blur1}Now we have a real victory here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:07.62,Op 2 - TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,690)\fad(200,200)\blur1}This is our first honor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.66,0:01:08.72,Op 2 - TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,690)\fad(200,200)\blur1}Now, my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:13.92,Op 2 - TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,690)\fad(200,200)\blur1}let's celebrate this victory to prepare for our next battle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:34.12,Op 2 - TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,690)\fad(200,200)\blur1}No death will be in vain
